Five people have been burnt beyond recognition in a horrific accident between Zastron and Sterkspruit on Friday.This comes after a head on collision between a mini bus taxi and bakkie, nine people dead and seven injured.According to rescue service injuries ranged to from minor to critical.&#8220;This morning nine people were killed and another seven sustained injuries ranging from minor to critical after a bakkie and minibus taxi collided head-on,&#8221; said Arrive Alive.&#8220;Five persons were burnt beyond recognition in the fire following the crash,&#8221; added Arrive Alive.Patients who sustained injuries were treated on scene by emergency workers before they were transported to various hospitals in the area.-TNA Reporter